About the project

This is the front-end website created for booking movie tickets. It is almost similar to the main website but does not require payment or store old data. If you cannot find an option to move to the next page, please ensure that you have selected all the necessary data on the current page. Once you have selected the required information, you will be provided with an option to proceed.

Technologies used in the project

Front-end technologies such as HTML, CSS, JavaScript and React to create the user interface. APIs to retrieve information such as movie data and casting details.
